casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. Sanchez, Appellant.

[Cite as State v. Sanchez (1996), 77 Ohio St.3d 1204.]

*1205(No. 96-730 Submitted October 9, 1996 Decided November 6, 1996.) Daniel D. Connor Co., L.P.A., and Daniel D. Connor, for appellant.

The appeal is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur. Stratton, J., not participating.
